                                    "title": null,
                                    "desc": {
                                        "html": "<p>Recap To build an open source culture you need: ● Grass root support ● One (or multiple) change agents (to light the fire and kindle it) ● Management support / Executive buy-in ● Lots of time OSPO can be there in support (Facebook) or be the change agent (Microsoft) Change can be top-down (Microsoft) or bottom-up (Facebook)</p>\n"
                                    },
                                    "image": "https://on.notist.cloud/slides/deck4284/large-43.png",
                                    "html": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "sl_eee9bz",
                                    "type": "image",
                                    "title": null,
                                    "desc": {
                                        "html": "<p>Recap What makes it sustainable? Alignment with company goals (i.e. a strategy): ● Break silos @ Microsoft ● Improve the company’s image and drive recruiting @ Facebook</p>\n"
                                    },
                                    "image": "https://on.notist.cloud/slides/deck4284/large-44.png",
                                    "html": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "sl_GyMxUO",
                                    "type": "image",
                                    "title": null,
                                    "desc": {
                                        "html": "<p>Open source isn’t a journey. It’s a practice.</p>\n"
                                    },
                                    "image": "https://on.notist.cloud/slides/deck4284/large-45.png",
                                    "html": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "sl_tI5lMn",
                                    "type": "image",
                                    "title": null,
                                    "desc": {
                                        "html": "<p>“Because I’ve made culture change at Microsoft such a high priority, people often ask how it’s going. Well, I suppose my response is very Eastern: We’re making great progress, but we should never be done. It’s not a program with a start and an end. It’s a way of being.” —Satya Nadella, CEO, Microsoft</p>\n"
